data.description: BACK on the MARKET due to the buyer not able to close... 4 BEDROOM / 2 bath / 2-car garage home!!! CITY WATER!!! X-FLOOD ZONE so no flood insurance is required by the lender!!! FENCED BACK YARD!!! 2022 water heater!!! 2018 HVAC!!! BRAND NEW CARPETING in all 4 bedrooms!!! New stainless microwave!!! New light fixtures and fans!!! New garbage disposal!!! New kitchen backsplash!!! New screening on FRONT enclosed entry!!! New LANAI screening!!! SECURITY ALARM!!! ADDITIONAL cabinetry storage in INTERIOR LAUNDRY ROOM! NEWLY SCREENED LANAI also is enclosed with "Florida Glass" windows for temperature and moisture control! GUTTERS all the way around the house!!! This fantastic home offers all the private space you desire with its GREAT ROOM and FOUR BEDROOMS. As you approach this property, notice the large front windows which allow natural light to infiltrate this home. Tall ceilings and an abundance of windows are here to greet you. Outside, MATURE TREES overlook the front and back yards. This INCREDIBLE HOME is close to schools and all the amenities. CRANBERRY ELEMENTARY is SUPER CLOSE!!! Cocoplum shopping center is 2-MINUTE DRIVE!!! Be at the North Port AQUATIC CENTER in 11 minutes!!! TAMPA BAY RAYS and the ATLANTA BRAVES baseball parks are in close proximity. ENGLEWOOD BEACH and MANASOTA BEACHES are a short 25 MINUTE DRIVE!!! HISTORIC PUNTA GORDA and the NEW SUNSEEKER RESORT is just a short drive south. YOU CANNOT BEAT THIS LOCATION and you CANNOT BEAT THIS VALUE!!!
